                            {
                                "type": "equation_inline",
                                "content": "\\lambda = 2"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": ". Does this imply that the scheme is stable for "
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "equation_inline",
                                "content": "\\lambda \\leq 2 ^ { \\cdot }"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": "? If not, find "
